name: StCloudState
0:
”Alexa, open Saint Cloud State”
”Alexa, ask Saint Cloud State what's happening this weekend?”
”Alexa, ask Saint Cloud State where Brown Hall is”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: saint cloud state
des: The Saint Cloud State University Alexa skill answers questions about what events are happening on campus and where to find campus buildings. You can even listen to Saint Cloud State's very own president give a welcome speech by saying "Alexa, ask Saint Cloud State to play the welcome message".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
